{"tid":2276292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［新國際線］今日開始打gab戰線","createTime":"2020-11-07T18:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T01:57:22.000Z","uid":82389,"like":70,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"aaea001b6b91d9a6c8fd8e781db224d69bc1e1e2","tid":2276292,"uid":82389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T18:01:00.000Z","msg":"1. 所有連登會員開帳戶<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 喺自己嘅Facebook同IG<br />\n每日一post宣傳gab [起碼要拉到2,000,000自己人入嚟]<br />\n<br />\n2b. 冇發夢嘅朋友，開帳戶嘅時候唔好用自己相<br />\n之後喺連登互相交朋友，盡量擴大同溫層<br />\n<br />\n3. KOL既 請自己拍YouTube片，不停洗腦式宣傳呢個app<br />\n<br />\n4. 每個人目標要幫到五個人去啟動呢個社交平台<br />\n<br />\n5. 黃店要用呢個社交平台，慢慢取代Facebook<br />\nIG<br />\n<br />\n6.每人搵三個外國人朋友裝呢個app<br />\n<br />\n7. 等到間公司有人口基礎可以喺美國上市<br />\n<br />\n8.你懂的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e04313d8385b98922a4cd01304ef44c2cebffbf","tid":2276292,"uid":82389,"like":16,"dislike":6,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T18:02:09.000Z","msg":"認真，呢個app<br />\n搞掂咗頭八個Steps後<br />\n<br />\n開始打台灣戰線，將台灣人拉埋入我哋同一陣線"},{"pid":"fa594e6b6f6313b0eb8c0fec717df8adf4f20f38","tid":2276292,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T18:02:21.000Z","msg":"join<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"861f38e41d88a9e353620168721c506155d23dea","tid":2276292,"uid":82389,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T18:04:28.000Z","msg":"幫手推，或者大家討論下可以點樣做去盡量擴闊呢個社交平台。<br />\n<br />\n當然如果單純post政治，大家都會悶<br />\n開咗ACC嘅朋友，可以搵返啲好笑嘢貼上去<br />\n<br />\n我都相信特朗普呢場官司未必打好耐<br />\n起碼我哋要幫佢頂到，詳官司完結，成件事完結為止"},{"pid":"8a1a6727242226b6965bfa39fd603048ee94046f","tid":2276292,"uid":29514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T18:04:36.000Z","msg":"3唔會做到, youtube唔會比你上架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8056f9d4c39677b523def1883b379f4d0024a7df","tid":2276292,"uid":82389,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2